TODO: Adjust the following lines from README

* install TMDlib source code;
    get code from https://tmdlib.hepforge.org/
    
    tar xvfz tmdlib.xxxxxx.tgz
    cd tmdlib.xxxxxx.
    ./configure --prefix=Path_to_install_TMDlib --with-lhapdf=Path_to_LHAPDF-6.2.X --with-gsl=Path_to_gsl-2.3.X
    make ; make install
    
    
* TMDgrid files are to be downloaded separetely
    Path_to_install_TMDlib/bin/TMDlib_getdata --help       -> description of download procedure
    Path_to_install_TMDlib/bin/TMDlib_getdata all          -> install all availbale TMDsets (take long !)
    Path_to_install_TMDlib/bin/TMDlib_getdata PB-NLO-2018  -> install PB-TMD sets
